Before I spoke a word, You were singing over me                            Prieš tai, kai prabilau, apglėbei giesme mane
You have been so, so good to me                                            Tu buvai toks toks geras man
Before I took a breath, You breathed Your life in me                       Man nekvėpuojant dar, tu įkvėpei gyvybę man
You have been so so kind to me                                             Tu buvai toks toks geras man
                                                                           
Oh, the overwhelming, never-ending, reckless love of God                   Oh galinga, begalinė, dovanota meilė Jo
Oh, it chases me down, fights 'til I'm found, leaves the 99                Oh ji ieško ir suranda pasiklydusį mane
And I couldn't earn it, I don't deserve it, still You give yourself away   Nors aš nevertas, nenusipelnęs, jis aukoja man save
Oh, the overwhelming, never-ending, reckless love of God                   Oh galinga, begalinė, dovanota meilė Jo
                                                                           
